title: 38: Eliminate Stress and Make Anxiety Disappear in Minutes
description:
In this episode I sit down with my good friend Nick Ortner to discuss "The Tapping Solution". For those of you who haven't heard of it, it's an absolute game changer. This is part 1 of 2 from our conversation, be on the lookout for the next episode this week!
